they were engaged,

00:02:45.990 --> 00:02:49.780 align:middle line:84%
enthusiastic, and also very
mature in their thinking.

00:02:49.780 --> 00:02:52.290 align:middle line:84%
The Green School is
an example of a school

00:02:52.290 --> 00:02:56.890 align:middle line:84%
that is learning itself from
different education systems.

00:02:56.890 --> 00:02:59.860 align:middle line:84%
