charge of their own learning

00:03:11.160 --> 00:03:12.190 align:middle line:90%
process.

00:03:12.190 --> 00:03:16.200 align:middle line:84%
All ideas were welcome as long
as the kids themselves figured

00:03:16.200 --> 00:03:17.480 align:middle line:90%
out how to make it happen.

