00:05:37.610 --> 00:05:45.450 align:middle line:90%


00:05:45.450 --> 00:05:48.450 align:middle line:84%
>> We wanted to create a school
that would feel like home

00:05:48.450 --> 00:05:49.740 align:middle line:90%
