00:05:49.740 --> 00:05:51.170 align:middle line:90%
Home for the parents.

00:05:51.170 --> 00:05:52.300 align:middle line:90%
Home for the kids.

00:05:52.300 --> 00:05:53.940 align:middle line:84%
Home for the teachers
