00:05:53.940 --> 00:05:57.060 align:middle line:84%
a community of loving people,
caring about one another

00:05:57.060 --> 00:06:01.300 align:middle line:90%
in a very meaningful way.

00:06:01.300 --> 00:06:04.890 align:middle line:84%
