00:06:12.310 --> 00:06:13.630 align:middle line:90%
It's a beautiful challenge.

00:06:13.630 --> 00:06:18.390 align:middle line:84%
You have such a wonderful blend
of incredibly gifted children.

00:06:18.390 --> 00:06:21.420 align:middle line:10%
And the teachers
at Green School are

00:06:21.420 --> 00:06:23.790 align:middle line:10%
teaching to children's
strengths, which

00:06:23.790 --> 00:06:27.030 align:middle line:10%
