doing well in a subject,

00:06:27.030 --> 00:06:29.620 align:middle line:10%
they must be doing well
in another subject.

00:06:29.620 --> 00:06:31.320 align:middle line:84%
And let's pull that
out of your child

00:06:31.320 --> 00:06:34.440 align:middle line:84%
and let's allow your child to
go home confident and feeling

00:06:34.440 --> 00:06:36.540 align:middle line:90%
proud every day.

00:06:36.540 --> 00:06:39.790 align:middle line:84%
So that's really what
we wanted to create.

00:06:39.790 --> 00:06:41.655 align:middle line:90%
We wanted to create a family.

00:06:41.655 --> 00:06:43.530 align:middle line:10%
If you can create the
opportunity for a child

00:06:43.530 --> 00:06:47.640 align:middle line:10%
to understand what gratitude is
and exercise it on a daily basis

00:06:47.640 --> 00:06:51.570 align:middle line:10%
with their parents,
that's really, truly

00:06:51.570 --> 00:06:55.860 align:middle line:10%
the making of
phenomenal human beings.

00:06:55.860 --> 00:06:57.930 align:middle line:84%
Because what's more
important to this world

00:06:57.930 --> 00:07:00.810 align:middle line:84%
than having people that are
actually paying attention

00:07:00.810 --> 00:07:03.940 align:middle line:84%
to what is in the moment,
living in the moment,

00:07:03.940 --> 00:07:07.150 align:middle line:84%
and understanding it and
having an appreciation for it?

00:07:07.150 --> 00:07:09.290 align:middle line:84%
That is only acquired
by reflection

00:07:09.290 --> 00:07:10.810 align:middle line:90%
at the end of the day.

00:07:10.810 --> 00:07:13.100 align:middle line:84%
The kids are passionate
about the planet.

00:07:13.100 --> 00:07:16.840 align:middle line:84%
The kids are interested in a
light footprint in their lives.

00:07:16.840 --> 00:07:21.730 align:middle line:84%
And the kids are interested
in integrity and respect

00:07:21.730 --> 00:07:25.360 align:middle line:90%
and community and creativity.

00:07:25.360 --> 00:07:29.140 align:middle line:84%
They know what it is to have
been loved during the time they

00:07:29.140 --> 00:07:31.630 align:middle line:84%
were at school by the
teachers, by the community,

00:07:31.630 --> 00:07:32.690 align:middle line:90%
by their family.

00:07:32.690 --> 00:07:34.960 align:middle line:84%
It takes a real act of
passionate commitment

00:07:34.960 --> 00:07:37.630 align:middle line:84%
for a family to pick
up and leave a country

00:07:37.630 --> 00:07:42.640 align:middle line:84%
to move here for the sake of
their children's education.

00:07:42.640 --> 00:07:47.230 align:middle line:84%
One of our recent graduates
started a little movement

00:07:47.230 --> 00:07:49.420 align:middle line:90%
called Jungalow Ecosystem.

00:07:49.420 --> 00:07:52.420 align:middle line:84%
They're encouraging people to
build forests in their homes,

00:07:52.420 --> 00:07:53.600 align:middle line:90%
in their gardens--

00:07:53.600 --> 00:07:56.620 align:middle line:84%
examples of how humans can
begin incorporating forests

00:07:56.620 --> 00:07:58.100 align:middle line:90%
into everything we do.

00:07:58.100 --> 00:08:01.180 align:middle line:84%
Not only do these trees provide
a cooler and cleaner environment

00:08:01.180 --> 00:08:03.640 align:middle line:84%
to play in, but they
also add extra elements

00:08:03.640 --> 00:08:07.540 align:middle line:84%
of imagination, creativity,
and fun of all sorts of games

00:08:07.540 --> 00:08:08.510 align:middle line:90%
to be played.

00:08:08.510 --> 00:08:10.518 align:middle line:84%
Not to mention trees
have been proven

00:08:10.518 --> 00:08:12.310 align:middle line:84%
to have great benefits
to the mental health

00:08:12.310 --> 00:08:13.850 align:middle line:90%
and well-being of kids.

00:08:13.850 --> 00:08:15.640 align:middle line:84%
So these Green School
kids are really

00:08:15.640 --> 00:08:19.780 align:middle line:84%
into making the world a
better place, tree by tree,

00:08:19.780 --> 00:08:23.140 align:middle line:84%
plant by plant, ecosystem by
ecosystem, one drop of water

00:08:23.140 --> 00:08:24.290 align:middle line:90%
after another.

00:08:24.290 --> 00:08:27.010 align:middle line:84%
It's really amazing and
remarkable that all of the Green

00:08:27.010 --> 00:08:29.380 align:middle line:84%
School grads are really
committed to making

00:08:29.380 --> 00:08:30.930 align:middle line:90%
the world a better place.

00:08:30.930 --> 00:08:34.860 align:middle line:90%


00:08:34.860 --> 00:08:38.429 align:middle line:84%
>> Improving our education
system is not just about

00:08:38.429 --> 00:08:41.620 align:middle line:90%
intangible benefits to society.

00:08:41.620 --> 00:08:43.950 align:middle line:84%
