on improving early child

00:08:43.950 --> 00:08:46.950 align:middle line:84%
development, the return
can be more than $8.

00:08:46.950 --> 00:08:51.070 align:middle line:84%
And this return-to-cost ratio
is highest in early childhood.

00:08:51.070 --> 00:08:52.620 align:middle line:84%
