00:18:49.800 --> 00:18:51.870 align:middle line:84%
in a really well-built
beautiful environment,

00:18:51.870 --> 00:18:54.335 align:middle line:84%
not a traditional
institutional framework.

00:18:54.335 --> 00:18:56.460 align:middle line:84%
>> The Green School has
changed my life and changed

00:18:56.460 --> 00:18:57.760 align:middle line:90%
my perspective.

