to be the end all,

00:19:58.720 --> 00:20:02.890 align:middle line:84%
but it was meant to be
a catalyst for change

00:20:02.890 --> 00:20:05.890 align:middle line:84%
around the world with
holistic education.

00:20:05.890 --> 00:20:07.690 align:middle line:84%
It's about building
with local materials.

00:20:07.690 --> 00:20:10.420 align:middle line:84%
It's about building
sustainably, something beautiful

00:20:10.420 --> 00:20:14.820 align:middle line:84%
and something that is serving
a need of a community.

